Jack Henderson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Henderson_(actor) 0 David John "Jack" Henderson (14 May 1877 – 1 January 1957) was an American silent film actor. Jack Henderson was born on 14 May 1877 or 1878 in Syracuse, New York.Henderson acted with Charlie Chaplin at Essanay Studios in Los Angeles from October 1915, and continued with him at Mutual.Henderson died on 1 January 1957 in New York City.
